These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: video-games, baking
The people have 2 different jobs:  bartender, police-officer
1. the bartender is in an even position##4
2. the police-officer is the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | baking | video-games |
| Job     | police-officer    | bartender   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, handball
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | lemonade        |
| Sport      | rowing  | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, dubstep
There are 2 different nationalities: german, spanish
1. the german is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of soul##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep    | soul |
| Nationality   | german | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, water
There 2 different types of food: peas, lime
1. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
2. the person eating lime is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | fanta      | water |
| Food       | peas | lime    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
